<ul  class="mgActionList" >
<li class='mgSocialShareButton'><span id='mg-ratings-button-container-A67127' class='mg-ratings-button-container-low '><button id='mg-ratings-button-A67127' onclick='AddLike("A", 67127, 1, 141084761); return false;' class='mg-ratings-button ' type='button' aria-live='polite' aria-busy='false' role='button' title='Click the button if this item matters to you' ><span id='mg-ratings-button-icon-wrapper-A67127' class='mg-ratings-button-icon-wrapper'><img id='mg-ratings-button-icon-A67127' class=' mg-ratings-button-icon mg-ratings-button-icon-subscribe ' src='mgimages/boxnotick.jpg' alt='Not checked.' title='' /></span><span class='mg-ratings-button-content subscribe-label'>This matters&#63;</span><span id='mg-subscription-button-subscriber-count-A67127' class='mg-subscription-button-subscriber-count '  title='The number of people this matters to'><span class='mgHide'>The number of people this matters to is </span><span class='mg-subscription-number'>0</span></span></button></span><div class='mgSocialShareButton'  data-link-to='http://moderngov.lambeth.gov.uk/mgAi.aspx?id=67127' data-post-title='Matters&#32;Arising&#32;and&#32;Work&#32;Programme&#32;2025&#47;26' data-post-image='http&#58;&#47;&#47;moderngov.lambeth.gov.uk&#47;mgimages&#47;mgLogo75.png'><button class='mgSocialShareLink' title='Click to share this item'><span class='mgHide' >Share this item</span></button><div id='mgSocialMenuA67127' class='mgSocialMenu'><ul><li><button title='Share with Twitter' class='mgShareTwitter' data-network='twitter'><span class='mgHide' >Share with Twitter</span></button></li><li><button title='Share with Facebook' class='mgShareFacebook' data-network='facebook'><span class='mgHide' >Share with Facebook</span></button></li><li><button title='Share with Google&#43;' class='mgShareGplus' data-network='gplus'><span class='mgHide'>Share with Google&#43;</span></button></li></ul></div></div></li>
</ul>
<p class="mgSubItemTitleTxt">Minutes:</p>
<div class="mgWordPara"><div class="WordSection1">
<p class="MsoNormal">Officers confirmed that the paper set out the
work programme for the remaining meetings in the current municipal
year. The report highlighted that a small number of amendments had
been made to the work programme for the January 2026 meeting,
including the addition of a new policy paper, which officers were
scheduled to introduce later in the agenda.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Several items had been removed from the agenda
for the January 2026 meeting and deferred to April 2026 meeting,
namely the final valuation results and the funding strategy update,
as these were not yet sufficiently developed or finalised. The
investment strategy item had also been removed, as its content had
been incorporated into one of the reports on the current
agenda.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">In addition, a paper presenting the outcome of
the governance review recently undertaken by Hymans Robertson had
been added to the April 2026 meeting. This paper would set out the
findings of the review, together with the associated
recommendations and a proposed action plan.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">A member sought an update on the actuarial
contract tender, which was not included in the work programme but
had been raised previously. Officers advised that a brief reference
would be made under the action tracker item and provided an update.
It had been concluded that a full re-tender exercise would be
required, as the previous tender process lacked sufficient
documentation to be relied upon or progressed.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Consequently, a new tender process would need
to be undertaken. Officers were unable to confirm a detailed
timetable at this stage, as this had not yet been fully developed,
particularly in light of competing work priorities, including the
Fit for the Future transition. However, the matter was considered a
priority.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Officers further noted that an initial review
of the current arrangements with the existing actuary would be
required to assess their adequacy and to consider whether interim
extension options were available. A new tender exercise would be
progressed in due course.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b>RESOLVED</b>:</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">The work programme was noted.</p>
</div>
</div> 
					
