<p class="mgSubItemTitleTxt">Minutes:</p>
<div class="mgWordPara"><div class="WordSection1">
<p class="MsoNormal">Officers reported that the tracker format had
been amended to show the status of each item as at the previous
meeting, enabling clearer comparison with the updates
presented.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">A small number of changes were highlighted.
Under the communications heading, several items had been marked as
complete. These related to the publication of the Annual Report,
which had been issued by the statutory deadline of 1 December 2025,
and the publication and submission of the Stewardship Code report
in accordance with the 31 October 2025 deadline.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Officers confirmed that the outcome of the
Stewardship Code submission had been received earlier that week and
was positive. The Fund had been accepted as a signatory to the Code
for a further year. It was noted that officers would seek to retain
this status when preparing the next submission later in the
year.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">A further amendment was noted in relation to
actuarial matters, reflecting that work to update the Funding
Strategy Statement was now underway, including the associated
employer consultation. Reference was also made to the sole item
marked as red on the tracker, relating to the actuarial contract,
which officers confirmed would be subject to a full re-tender
exercise.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Members referred to the action item marked in
red, &ldquo;Plan and prepare for the re-tender of the actuarial
services contract&rdquo;, noting that the contractual position had
not been met. However, it was acknowledged that this issue had been
addressed in officers&rsquo; earlier comments and that appropriate
action was in progress.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b>RESOLVED</b>:</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">The Business Plan Tracker was noted.</p>
</div>
