<p class="mgSubItemTitleTxt">Additional documents:</p>

<ul  class="mgBulletList" >
						    <li>
						    <a  href="documents/s173271/09.1 Appendix One - Lambeth Investment Performance Report - Q3 2025.pdf"  target="mgDocument173271" title="Link to document &#39;09.1 Appendix One - Lambeth Investment Performance Report - Q3 2025&#39; pdf file">09.1 Appendix One - Lambeth Investment Performance Report - Q3 2025 <span  class="mgHide" >, item 9.</span>
						    <span  class="mgFileSize" ><img height="12" src="mgimages/logo-pdf-1.gif" width="12" alt="pdf icon" /> PDF 569 KB</span> </a>  </li>

